title: FULL SHOW: We Chat With Roland Martin, Talk Kanye, Chat With Toosi and More
itunes:title: FULL SHOW: We Chat With Roland Martin, Talk Kanye, Chat With Toosi and More
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club we chat with Roland Martin about everything politics. Later during the Rumor Report Angela gives us the latest with Kanye West. And to wrap the show we chat with our friend Toosi about his new project "Boy's Dont Cry".
